    <string name="privacy_content"><![CDATA[
        Last Update: 2026

        1. Information We Collect
        BoostHabits collects basic information from your Google account (name, email, and profile picture) and physical activity data if you grant permission to Health Connect. This includes steps, distance, calories burned, and exercise sessions.

        2. Use of Information
        Your data is used exclusively for:
        - Syncing your habits across devices via Firebase.
        - Calculating your progress in real-time and awarding rewards (Gems and Coins).
        - Personalizing your user experience (themes, frames, and avatars).
        - Displaying your position on the global leaderboard.

        3. Security and Storage
        We use Firebase to store your data securely. We implement robust encryption and authentication measures. We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties for advertising purposes.

        4. Health Connect Integration
        BoostHabits acts as a viewer and aggregator of your health data. We do not generate this data directly but read it from your device\'s health database to automate your sports habit fulfillment.

        5. Your Rights
        You have the right to access, rectify, or delete your personal data. You can request the permanent deletion of your account and all associated data from the Settings section.
    ]]></string>

    <string name="legal_content"><![CDATA[
        BoostHabits - Healthy Habit Management Application.

        1. Intellectual Property
        All intellectual property rights for the content of this application and its graphic design are the exclusive property of BoostHabits.

        2. Liability
        BoostHabits is not responsible for injuries or health problems resulting from performing the suggested physical activities. Consult with a professional before starting any intense exercise routine.

        3. Use of the Application
        The user agrees to make diligent use of the application and the services accessible from it.
    ]]></string>

    <string name="help_content"><![CDATA[
        BoostHabits Help and Support Center

        1. Habit Management
        - Create: Press the center \'+\' button to choose a category and a habit.
        - Complete: Manual habits require pressing the \'Done\' button. Physical activity habits are automatically completed if synced with Health Connect.
        - Edit/Delete: Long-press a habit on the home list or access details to modify it.

        2. Economy System (Gems and Coins)
        - Gems: Earned with \'Physical Activity\' habits. Used to redeem real discount coupons in the shop.
        - Coins: Earned with other habits. Used to buy cosmetics (frames, backgrounds, and styles).

        3. Profile Personalization
        Go to \'Rewards\' to buy a cosmetic. Once purchased, it will appear in your inventory. From \'Profile\' -> \'Personalization\', you can equip or unequip your acquisitions. Wallpapers also change the color theme of the entire application.

        4. Health Sync (Health Connect)
        If your steps or exercises do not appear, check the following:
        - You have the \'Android Health\' or \'Health Connect\' app installed.
        - You have granted read permissions to BoostHabits in Health Settings.
        - The app recording the exercise (e.g., Google Fit, Samsung Health) is writing the data correctly to Health Connect.

        5. Contact
        If you experience any technical errors or have a suggestion, you can write to us at:
        Email: support@boosthabits.com
        Hours: Monday to Friday, 9:00 - 18:00.
    ]]></string>
